screen_desc: The screenshot shows a product page on Newegg for Razer headphones. There is an option to protect the purchase with an Allstate Protection Plan, which covers product breakdowns, includes easy online claims 24/7, offers a 5-day service guarantee, and provides 100% parts and labor coverage with no deductibles. There are two plans available: a 3-year plan for $17.99 (about $0.50 per month) and a 4-year plan for $21.99 (about $0.46 per month). There is also an "ADD" button to purchase the protection plan.
